1.10
log
@Just return if nmemb is 0.  Avoids a NULL dereference and is
consistent with the behavior of the other libc sort functions.
OK deraadt@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: merge.c,v 1.9 2011/03/06 00:55:38 deraadt Exp $ */
/*-
